IF NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM #SkipChecks WHERE DatabaseName IS NULL AND CheckID = 21 ) BEGIN IF @@VERSION NOT LIKE '%Microsoft SQL Server 2000%' AND @@VERSION NOT LIKE '%Microsoft SQL Server 2005%' BEGIN SET @StringToExecute = 'INSERT INTO #BlitzResults (CheckID, DatabaseName, Priority, FindingsGroup, Finding, URL, Details) SELECT 21 AS CheckID, [name] as DatabaseName, 200 AS Priority, ''Informational'' AS FindingsGroup, ''Database Encrypted'' AS Finding, ''http://BrentOzar.com/go/tde'' AS URL, (''Database ['' + [name] + ''] has Transparent Data Encryption enabled. Make absolutely sure you have backed up the certificate and private key, or else you will not be able to restore this database.'') AS Details FROM sys.databases WHERE is_encrypted = 1 and name not in (select distinct DatabaseName from #SkipChecks)' EXECUTE(@StringToExecute) END; END
